  <prompt>
    Configure the Invoice Review Queue Dataverse view on the sprk_invoice entity. The view should filter for invoices with sprk_status = ToReview (pending human review after classification). Columns: sprk_invoicenumber, sprk_vendororgid (lookup display), sprk_matterid (lookup display), sprk_invoicedate, sprk_totalamount, sprk_currency, sprk_recordtype, sprk_extractionstatus, createdon. Sort by createdon descending (newest first). Name the view "Invoice Review Queue" and set as a public view accessible to the Finance team.
  </prompt>

  <role>
