  <notes>
    The review queue view is the primary way human reviewers interact with classified invoices in MVP. Future upgrades may include a PCF Dataset control for a richer review experience.

    Reviewers use this view to:
    1. See newly classified invoices
    2. Verify or correct matter/vendor assignments
    3. Confirm the invoice (which triggers extraction via the confirm endpoint)

    The sprk_extractionstatus column helps reviewers see which invoices have already been processed (NotRun = awaiting confirmation, Extracted = already processed, Failed = needs attention).
